data.description: Nestled on a Large corner lot, this cozy ranch is an amazing opportunity!! Located just a short distance from shopping, bases, ship yards, and interstate this property has everything you need. New Nest thermostat, Security System, and Freshly Painted. Great for the first time homebuyer or investor looking to expand residential income portfolio. Home being sold AS IS, priced to sell, seller willing to perform appraisal repairs. Large detached one car garage can be used for just about anything your heart desires. Don't let this one get away
